@@ -1,2 +1,13 @@
 import gradio as gr
 
+def soma(num1, num2):
+    return num1 + num2
+
+iface = gr.Interface(
+    fn = soma,
+    inputs = ["number", "number"]
+    outputs = "number"
+    title = "Soma números"
+)
+
+iface.launch()
